  "prompt": "What does it mean to \"contribute to society?\"",
  "response": "To \"contribute to society\" means to take actions or engage in behaviors that benefit the community or the world at large. This can be done in numerous ways, such as through volunteering, charitable giving, participating in community events or organizations, or pursuing a career that has a positive impact on society. Contributing to society involves using one's skills, resources, and time to help others and improve the collective well-being of a community or the world.",
